title: Windows 8.1 RTM Activator pro  & enterprise (x64 x86) -=[Haj
description:
ENGLISH:

Windows 8.1 RTM Activator Kit :

(((((Disable Internet )))))

1.REMOVE installation key first using "Winact 1.4.1" (Right Click "Run as administrator")

[img]http://img12.imageshack.us/img12/9137/1u6i.png[/img]

- Choose "options" and "unistall product key".

2.Run A9600E (for x64 A9600E.bat) (Right Click "Run as administrator") and wait.

[img]http://img837.imageshack.us/img837/2307/3b0j.png[/img]

- Check your Computer properties, Windows is now activated.

3.Run "My WCP watermark Editor" (Right Click "Run as administrator")

[img]http://img826.imageshack.us/img826/8649/e2ji.png[/img]

- Check the box "Remove all wathermark" and click on "Apply new settings"

Done !, your Windows 8.1 RTM is now activated.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ALBANIAN :

Windows 8.1 RTM Activator Kit :

((((Ndale Internetin))))

1.Fshie key-in aktual ne windows duke e perdor "Winact 1.4.1" (mos harro me klick te djatht "Run as administrator")

- Zgjidh options dhe shkojm te "unistall product key".

2.Run A9600E (for x64 A9600E.bat) (me Klick te djatht "Run as administrator") dhe prit (deri sa te kryhet vet puna)

- Tash shko te Computer Propertis me shiqu a eshte "Windows is now activated".

3.Run "My WCP watermark Editor" (gjithmon me klick te djatht te mausit "Run as administrator")

- selekto katrorin "Remove all wathermark" dhe kliko ne "Apply new settings"

Gjithcka perfundoj windows 8.1 RTM eshte Aktivizuar.
